Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.45,0:00:03.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\be1}{\fnArial Black\pos(316,325)\fad(400,0)}Obey the Rules and manners\Nto have a fun Duel!!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:16.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Worried that this full tank of energy will lose it's destination
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.68,0:00:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Whoever shakes for just a minute their boredom, will explode!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.82,0:00:28.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I ride, atop the white line, Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.90,0:00:34.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Sit down, in the place you have faith Oh, Oh, Oh
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.91,0:00:38.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Go to the place that tempts you!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.30,0:00:44.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If each person took one thing at a time, freedom and passion in their hand
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.56,0:00:50.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}For the shine to come, continue our journey
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:56.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unclear everyday trump-card that sustains me, is your soul
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.89,0:01:02.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The best growth is coming forth, unstoppable wild drive
Dialogue: 0,0:01:02.95,0:01:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We are both yet to settle down, striking the door
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.80,0:01:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Noah, you won't be able to surpass me just by calling yourself a "creator" so you can come to terms with your pitiful past!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.94,0:01:30.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Even if your Deck Master is the best there is,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.48,0:01:32.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I will just have to be even greater!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.48,0:01:34.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm done with the pity farces.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.11,0:01:36.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's about time we put an end to this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.82,0:01:38.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What?! Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.07,0:01:41.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You mean to block my path?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.99,0:01:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Save Mokuba! The Fateful Seventh Turn"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.63,0:01:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.22,0:02:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like Mokuba's forgotten all about you after I took the liberty of sealing his memories away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.10,0:02:11.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Any enemy of my brother's is an enemy of mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.48,0:02:13.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.82,0:02:15.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.19,0:02:16.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're not going to attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.86,0:02:21.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you attack me using the effects of Dragon's Imperial Wrath, my Life will be ancient history!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.45,0:02:25.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But can you do that at the risk of harming Mokuba through the battle damage in the process?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.87,0:02:27.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Low life...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.08,0:02:29.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That damn bastard...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:32.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's time for you to get on with your attack already, Seto.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.17,0:02:38.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The fact is, Noah hasn't shown us a single flaw in this Duel.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.59,0:02:41.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} lets this opportunity go, he may not get another chance to win...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.26,0:02:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But even so...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.47,0:02:44.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.47,0:02:50.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.44,0:02:52.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.32,0:02:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It sure {\i1}is{\i0}, isn't it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.65,0:02:59.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not a thing you can do to oppose me now!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.82,0:03:06.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that awaits you is a cruel and painful future where I take your body and all you stand for!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.04,0:03:07.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You did well, Mokuba.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.75,0:03:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Get back over here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.46,0:03:15.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My beloved little brother, watch carefully as I dispose of him.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.67,0:03:17.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Right, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.34,0:03:22.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn! And the fourth turn of the creation of Heaven and Earth!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.80,0:03:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will now be activating the third Holy Ability of my Deck Master, Ark of Miracles!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.14,0:03:29.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Third Holy Ability?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.27,0:03:33.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. It's the third Holy Ability of the Ark of Miracles.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.31,0:03:34.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that is...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.69,0:03:36.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Restoration!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.66,0:03:45.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Monsters in the ark...!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.33,0:03:53.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Restoration...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.46,0:03:58.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If I remove all the Monsters in the Ark of Miracles from the game...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.55,0:04:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can increase my Life Points by 500 for each one.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.30,0:04:07.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had six Monsters on board the ark.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.64,0:04:11.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As such, my Life will recover by 6000 points.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.44,0:04:21.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah's Life rose to 6400!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.15,0:04:25.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he had just used Life Restoration from the beginning,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.66,0:04:30.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he wouldn't have needed to use Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0} as a shield, but he wanted to make Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} suffer!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.29,0:04:31.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That scum bag...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.87,0:04:33.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And then, a Magic Card...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.71,0:04:35.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I activate Black Hole!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.00,0:04:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This Magic Card destroys all Monsters on the field!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.39,0:04:53.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now more Monsters have entered the ark...!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.56,0:04:57.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's set up an infinite loop with his Absolute Protection and his Life Restoration.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.31,0:05:00.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's like that Deck Master is invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.32,0:05:02.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way to win this match, ooh!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I think my turn's over.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.20,0:05:06.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong, Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.82,0:05:08.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your turn now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.57,0:05:09.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.58,0:05:15.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I promised that I would be your\N father from now on... That I would protect you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.16,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's true that I was rough with you on that day...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.13,0:05:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Big brother...?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Just how far\N do you think I'll tolerate this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.00,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I did it so that in the worst case scenario, if I were to fail, you would still be a member of the Kaiba's.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.84,0:05:22.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Big brother, please believe me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.55,0:05:23.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1\an8}Silence!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.55,0:05:26.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Throw him out of here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.88,0:05:29.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But I didn't use you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.14,0:05:34.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I give my two cards to my big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.39,0:05:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And the two of us pulled something off that baffled the minds of everyone in that room.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.77,0:05:42.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our bond was strong\N enough to beat Gozaburo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.07,0:05:46.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It was our willingness to believe in one another that saved us!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.37,0:05:52.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.33,0:05:57.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There has to be a way I can save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.46,0:06:00.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}, you have to believe in Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.38,0:06:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.96,0:06:05.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I had to fight against Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} when Malik set up that trap for us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.88,0:06:10.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And it was my bond with Jounouchi-{\i1}kun{\i0} that saved us in that pinch.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.39,0:06:11.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to keep fighting.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.89,0:06:17.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to keep fighting, and you have to bring back your memories with Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.39,0:06:19.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Our bond...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.02,0:06:19.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}We have one!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.81,0:06:23.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a card that represents the bond between me and Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.98,0:06:26.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your friend sure gave you a hell of a tip.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.94,0:06:28.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't misinterpret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.65,0:06:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I take no orders from anyone but myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.99,0:06:34.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I fight everything on my own!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.12,0:06:36.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.45,0:06:38.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't it!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.29,0:06:42.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Return to our dimension,\N Twilight Zone Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.92,0:06:47.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I switch Twilight Zone Dragon into Defense Mode!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.34,0:06:51.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll end my turn with that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.09,0:06:53.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the fifth turn of creation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.98,0:07:05.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The field is changing again!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.27,0:07:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Eventually all living creatures on the planet began to undergo rapid evolution cycles.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.41,0:07:13.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Modern civilization was born as a result!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.20,0:07:18.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look, big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.70,0:07:20.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba Corporation...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:27.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, that is the castle I should be reigning in... Kaiba Corporation!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.17,0:07:29.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Time has reached its present.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:35.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, allow me to show you the most terrifying weapons in Kaiba Corporation's arsenal and the potential they wield.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.22,0:07:39.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Super Dimension Fighter Vic Viper, prepare for launch!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.03,0:07:59.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And now for the Magic Card Cyclone Laser!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:10.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then equip it with Matter Leveler.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.76,0:08:18.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If the Monster equipped with Matter Leveler attacks an opponent's Defense Position Monster,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.35,0:08:22.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the card's Attack Power automatically rises to 100 points more than that Monster's Defense Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.14,0:08:28.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Cyclone Laser is a card that inflicts damage to my opponent when I attack a Monsters with Defense Power lower than its Attack Power.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.23,0:08:31.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The target is Twilight Zone Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.44,0:08:33.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire the Cyclone Laser!!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.87,0:08:48.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Twilight Zone Dragon is a Monster that can't be destroyed by magic or in battle, isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:52.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the {\i1}perfect{\i0} Monster\N to torture you with!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.22,0:08:59.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That Noah freak's just gonna keep attacking Kaiba until he loses, OOH!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.14,0:09:01.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba, do something already!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.47,0:09:02.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.64,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn, draw!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.35,0:09:08.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This isn't the card either!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.06,0:09:13.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll leave Twilight Zone Dragon in Defense Position and end my turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.03,0:09:14.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, of {\i1}course{\i0} you will.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.65,0:09:18.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not a thing you need to do, other than thoroughly accept the suffering I'm going to hand you, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.95,0:09:22.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to enjoy the look of agony on your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.91,0:09:31.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't believe you have the gall to call yourself a creator when you get sick pleasure from watching people suffer.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.34,0:09:35.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I guess Gozaburo had a {\i1}reason{\i0} for abandoning you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.72,0:09:36.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.93,0:09:39.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father had faith in me\N all the way to his death!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.43,0:09:42.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I worked so hard for my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.64,0:09:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's not a time in my life that I betrayed his expectations!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.10,0:09:49.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will be reborn as a human being with superior knowledge!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.94,0:09:54.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll complete the Kaiba empire my father failed to establish!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.57,0:09:57.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Father will happily cheer me on!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.70,0:10:01.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And he'll say, "I knew it all along, Noah. You are my one and only son."
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:04.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the sixth turn of creation!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.00,0:10:07.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I Summon Option!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.17,0:10:15.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Option is a card that mimics the Attack and Defense Points of a Vic Viper on the field with its Special Ability.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.63,0:10:18.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Option, transform into Vic Viper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.89,0:10:24.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire the Cyclone Laser!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.90,0:10:38.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now watch carefully Mokuba, as we reveal our enemy for who he truly is!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.57,0:10:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.24,0:10:43.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't it hurt, Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.33,0:10:44.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It really does hurt, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:47.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Being betrayed by the one you love!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.83,0:10:53.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I still have a Monster\N that is yet to attack you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.38,0:10:54.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Vic Viper!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.92,0:10:56.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fire the Cyclone Laser!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.59,0:11:36.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a nice expression, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.30,0:11:38.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go to hell, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.21,0:11:40.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up, Kaiba! Don't give up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.59,0:11:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your mouth shut, Deadbeat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:45.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't need {\i1}you{\i0} of all people ordering me around!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.85,0:11:47.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba! You jerk!!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.64,0:11:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.39,0:11:50.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,An argument amongst friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.77,0:11:54.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Human beings are known to become weak of heart right before they lose everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.19,0:11:59.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, I think I'll put you out of your misery and finish you off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.36,0:12:02.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You agree, don't you Mokuba?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.20,0:12:04.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}, are you alright with this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.78,0:12:06.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doing all this to Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.87,0:12:11.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Haven't you and Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0} always helped each other out, no matter what's happened?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.41,0:12:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't your bond with him absolute?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.88,0:12:20.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He couldn't have cracked the seal on his memories...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.34,0:12:21.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.42,0:12:26.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This turn very well might be my last.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.51,0:12:29.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way I can fight you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.10,0:12:33.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As long as you're by my side, I can continue to fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.85,0:12:38.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that won't change, neither now or in the future!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.02,0:12:39.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba, bring them back!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.94,0:12:41.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Surface your memories!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.36,0:12:48.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All that awaited us at the Kaiba home was a living hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.12,0:12:51.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I thought of giving up\N countless times.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.25,0:12:54.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But then you gave me your cards.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.75,0:12:58.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}They're all trashy cards...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:13:01.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That was what saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.63,0:13:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,While staring at the paper card you made for me, I swore to myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That I would get the real one someday!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.68,0:13:12.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That the card was the best suited card for a real man!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.75,0:13:37.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.83,0:13:43.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you hadn't made that card for me, I would have been done for.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:48.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But do I really deserve that manly card, and to be your brother for that matter?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.68,0:13:54.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.89,0:13:58.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My deck is linked directly to Mokuba!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.49,0:14:07.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I place one set card!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.15,0:14:11.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll then activate Kaiser Sea Horse's Deck Master Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.08,0:14:15.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Twilight Dragon counts as two Tributes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.50,0:14:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Come forth!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.12,0:14:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.99,0:14:52.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.07,0:14:53.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.03,0:14:53.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.91,0:14:56.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why am I...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.66,0:14:59.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The seal on his memories broke...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:02.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba! Get away from him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.04,0:15:04.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were being controlled by him, OOH-AH!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.75,0:15:06.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah! You...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.42,0:15:09.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now's your chance, Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.09,0:15:10.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take this, Noah!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.51,0:15:14.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,BURST STREAM OF DESTRUCTION!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.52,0:15:26.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Noah's Life Points took a serious hit!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.36,0:15:30.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And Option is automatically destroyed the moment Vic Viper is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.95,0:15:34.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, I praise you for being able to injure me this much!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm invincible!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ark of Miracles!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.41,0:15:40.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Life Restoration!!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.21,0:15:48.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shit...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah's Life went up again...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.13,0:15:52.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here comes your end, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.76,0:15:54.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My turn!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.48,0:16:01.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've been waiting for this moment, Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.48,0:16:04.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is where we {\i1}truly{\i0} settles things between the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.98,0:16:05.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.94,0:16:08.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Me or you - who will win?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.28,0:16:09.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is the final round!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.69,0:16:12.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Trap Card, activate!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.03,0:16:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.41,0:16:18.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.58,0:16:27.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last Battle's effect...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.67,0:16:30.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I select a Monster on the field
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.38,0:16:35.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I then send every card albeit the one I chose to the Graveyard!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.26,0:16:40.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You are then to Summon a Monster from your deck that will engage in battle with mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.68,0:16:47.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This card makes it so that whoever's Monster remains alone on the field automatically wins the Duel, regardless of their Life Points.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.02,0:16:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So it basically determines the outcome of this battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.23,0:16:51.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba's taking a huge gamble here!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:54.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Naturally, I'll be choosing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.28,0:16:56.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Blue-Eyes White Dragon!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.45,0:17:00.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll choose my Deck Master,\N the Ark of Miracles!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.87,0:17:07.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, take mine and Mokuba's anger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.92,0:17:09.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Go, Blue-Eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.46,0:17:11.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Toward our future!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.17,0:17:14.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Burst Stream of Destruction!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.06,0:17:21.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.11,0:17:30.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.95,0:17:37.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What in the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.70,0:17:41.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's...?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.08,0:17:49.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's {\i1}hardly{\i0} enough to beat {\i1}me{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:57.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Be gone, Seto!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.68,0:18:04.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.85,0:18:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Have you {\i1}forgotten{\i0}, Seto?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.69,0:18:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That this was the seventh turn of the creation of Heaven and Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.15,0:18:20.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the turn that my Deck Master, Ark of Miracles, activates its {\i1}final{\i0} Special Ability!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.03,0:18:23.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,My Deck Master has revealed to you its true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.66,0:18:25.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shinato, King of Heaven!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.45,0:18:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And, as creator,\N I rise to the throne of God!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.54,0:18:31.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah's body...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.96,0:18:35.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This is my true form!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.09,0:18:40.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Last Battle automatically disregards our Life scores.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.93,0:18:43.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That battle just now determined the outcome of our Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.93,0:18:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto, the result is here!!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.18,0:18:49.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Father, are you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.23,0:18:53.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I just proved that I'm better at Seto in everything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.23,0:18:56.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Big brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.19,0:18:59.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm so sorry! It's all my fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.15,0:19:00.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.78,0:19:04.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seto! Mokuba! I hereby deliver onto thee Heaven's Judgment!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.92,0:19:11.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}! Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.71,0:19:14.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.09,0:19:14.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mokuba!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.96,0:19:17.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How lovely!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.51,0:19:20.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A pair so close, yet never able to touch one another.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.55,0:19:25.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I hereby give this piece of art the name, "Wonder Brotherhood"!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.85,0:19:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}... Mokuba-{\i1}kun{\i0}...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.98,0:19:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You bastard! You toyed with Kaiba's feelings and went so far as to use Mokuba as a shield!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.40,0:19:43.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doesn't your heart hurt, even just a little?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.62,0:19:46.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It was all a part of my studies!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.04,0:19:48.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All for my complete victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.37,0:19:50.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Complete victory", you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.12,0:19:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're{\i0} the one who lost in this Duel!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.08,0:19:55.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.59,0:20:00.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kaiba had played Twilight Zone Dragon in his turn just now,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.09,0:20:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Monster wouldn't have been able to be destroyed in battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.30,0:20:09.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If Kaiba hadn't Summoned Blue-Eyes, he would've prevailed by the effects of Last Battle!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.73,0:20:14.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba through away his desire to win and Summoned his Blue-Eyes out of love!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.23,0:20:16.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So he could get Mokuba's heart back!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.69,0:20:21.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah! If that was {\i1}you{\i0} up there, would you have chosen the same thing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.36,0:20:28.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A sad child who can't even comprehend the basics of human nature wanting to run Kaiba Corporation...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.04,0:20:29.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make me laugh!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.04,0:20:30.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You worm!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.37,0:20:36.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kaiba still has some of his Life remaining.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.42,0:20:40.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to be the true victor, battle with {\i1}me{\i0} now!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.05,0:20:40.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.42,0:20:44.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh? So you intend to take over Kaiba's Duel in such a situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.59,0:20:50.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll inherit Kaiba's entire deck, along with Mokuba's sadness!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.02,0:20:52.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Very well then.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.18,0:20:56.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be reckless, Yugi! You're talking his 7400 Life Points against your 400 here!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.65,0:20:58.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And you don't even have a hand, OOH!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be beaten in one attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.36,0:21:05.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you wish it so, I'll be happy to dispose of you, Yugi Mutou!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.28,0:21:06.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.21,0:21:28.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah, I won't let you get away with tarnishing Kaiba's and Mokuba's names with your cold-blooded heart!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.47,0:21:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,DUEL!!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.77,0:21:43.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,With Kaiba-{\i1}kun{\i0}'s deck and only a few Life Points to fight with,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.03,0:21:44.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi engages in a Duel with Noah.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.82,0:21:50.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Noah reorganizes his deck with a new type of Monster known as Spirit Monsters to attack Yugi with.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:50.91,0:21:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yugi sees their Special Effects for the first time!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.87,0:21:57.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You have to stand strong, even with such little Life and as you're beaten to a pulp, Yugi!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:59.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A chance will come sooner or later!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.38,0:22:00.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Next time!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.92,0:22:03.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"The Inherited Deck: Yugi VS Noah"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.67,0:22:05.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Duel standby!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.99,0:22:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, wherever it rises
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.90,0:22:23.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A dream is a dream, and it won't stop
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.17,0:22:28.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The straight rail and the steep route
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.85,0:22:33.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To go, or not go all of yourself
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.24,0:22:40.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm getting tired of counting my advances in a cage
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.80,0:22:44.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Respect! Boys, show me your strength
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.39,0:22:49.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's awkward, but draw the map
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.16,0:22:59.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now let's walk forever with our head up high...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.31,0:23:07.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The unsinkable sun, if it starts to get to familiar like you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.12,0:23:15.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}answer freely to the everyday discomfort
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.90,0:23:23.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I want to believe you, because I am losing my way with everything
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.88,0:23:33.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Hiding in my heart... this secret paradise
